    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Octopress is a great blog framework. One can start blogging in a few minutes using the github for the static pages/posts hosting.</p>

<p><code>
git clone git://github.com/imathis/octopress.git octopress
cd octopress/
bundle install
rake install
rake setup_github_pages
rake generate
rake deploy
</code></p>
